Handling Templates

1. Create a folder inside project, folder name -> templates
   Inside templates, better to create seperate folder for each app
2. Add the templates folder in to settings
   Object name TEMPLATES, inside this key DIRS

Jinja2 template syntax



file:////Users/kuthbudin/PycharmProjects/Akshara47/Akshara3/test1.html?user=ajay&passw=p123

Date passed using form written in test1 -> is passed via url
2 Kind request => GET & POST
by default, method is GET..
if the method is GET, data is passed via URL like a string
DO not use GET for secured info like passw, files

POST -> encrypts data and sends..
Data is not visible in the URL

action => if action not given in form, it will come to same page
